data.description: Situated on a gorgeous level lot, this darling single-level, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is located in the fantastic Hunters Glen subdivision. Inside you will find a lovely open concept with beautiful flooring throughout. There are vaulted ceilings in the kitchen, dining, and living areas. The master bedroom suite has a large vanity with plenty of linen storage, a garden tub, a shower, and a walk-in closet. This backyard is nicely maintained and perfect for entertaining friends or an awesome play space for your children. Hunters Glen has great amenities including a pool, a pavilion, and privacy fencing around the entire neighborhood.
